{"tid":2131134,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"莊太量政：GDP按年跌9%遜預期 政府不應再提供補貼","createTime":"2020-07-29T15:38:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T09:45:50.000Z","uid":225931,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"228f452b49d9722a964ea2fc0ce375e390a6d574","tid":2131134,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T15:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0E539eM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0E539eM.jpg&h=534204f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中大經濟學系副教授莊太量表示，是次跌幅遜於預期，主要受私人消費開支和固定資本跌幅加劇拖累，加上政府消費開支增加所致，可幸的是目前香港經濟仍是錄得單位數跌幅，較澳門第一季經濟按年下跌48.7%，及新加坡第二季經濟按年下跌12.6%表現較佳。<br />\n<br />\n莊太量估計港府禁止堂食將使私人消費開支進一步下挫，「啲人出唔到黎食飯，都唔會點行商場、買嘢」，不過，他預料第三季經濟只會按年下跌6%，皆因去年第三季經濟已經收縮2.9%，在基數較低情況下，預料第三季經濟按年跌幅不如第二季這麼大。<br />\n<br />\n他估計全年香港經濟將會下挫約7%；並指出在資源有限之下，政府不應再向各行各業作補貼，反而待疫情好轉後，撤回限制社交距離措施，並重新開關，這樣才能讓經濟復甦。"},{"pid":"4a5db4fd15cb052fd35fcbeb6495233e0e4aa40d","tid":2131134,"uid":70888,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T15:39:54.000Z","msg":"派錢呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"a24ef5cd75dde9c69c7584ee640e9f897518c5af","tid":2131134,"uid":2607,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T15:40:27.000Z","msg":"莊太量呢條撚樣邨未死"},{"pid":"fad273e8d95128e7a8e5f5460453c2ba516a8b16","tid":2131134,"uid":39777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T15:41:59.000Z","msg":"唔派錢咪開始裁員囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb517c9036e2b42c895620d107797707c5194a6c","tid":2131134,"uid":69872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T15:42:01.000Z","msg":"疫情好轉 重新開關<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？ <br />\n<br />\n咁撚樣囉 一日冇疫苗 點同你開關呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef0ce857d4873d02c72df87ebcc24182fb87459","tid":2131134,"uid":142388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T15:42:02.000Z","msg":"CU好多人都好憎莊太量 真係唔係無原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a6caa05bb7704ff028e0fc8381a79ea054f4d0","tid":2131134,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T15:42:37.000Z","msg":"呢條垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023db8042cf29c0bc3a27a8d0245c870f712f23d","tid":2131134,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T15:43:18.000Z","msg":"經濟學家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a632f37cf2797a44beb2f6807d97b12429f42db","tid":2131134,"uid":9435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T15:49:05.000Z","msg":"派錢未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6425e7f6ca376385e66a59ac9b4c04b67e55bc5e","tid":2131134,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T01:58:38.000Z","msg":"金融肺炎，勁過金融海嘯"},{"pid":"62e5470f569c518040b5d24af197f16815fe2138","tid":2131134,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:56:36.000Z","msg":"Gogogo"},{"pid":"c347c74e48490259b3e43680ee1334f2521e0755","tid":2131134,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T08:02:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4e52f1673deac47793c154782628e17a7f330324","tid":2131134,"uid":39872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":